title: La Fiesta en Hapeville | 05/17/2025 5:00 PM | Creative Loafing
description:
La Fiesta en Hapeville returns to Jess Lucas Park on Saturday, May 17, transforming downtown Hapeville into a vibrant celebration of Latin culture!

This year’s entertainment includes live music by Tulum Acoustics, storytelling by Naty and high-energy Latin salsa tunes from Atlanta Show Band Live Latin Salsa. Come savor authentic Latin cuisine from local food vendors, test your skills on the mechanical bull, challenge friends to a game of human-sized foosball, get your face painted and take part in many more family-friendly activities. With free admission and parking, La Fiesta en Hapeville offers a lively cultural experience for all ages in the heart of Hapeville.
